4. **CRUD per entity**: Estimates, customers, inventory, equipment, settings — all company-scoped
5. **Edge Functions**: Complete-job deducts inventory correctly; mark-paid calculates P&L
6. **Storage**: Upload PDF → path includes company_id → other company blocked
7. **Realtime**: Two tabs — crew logs time, admin sees it instantly
8. **Permissions**: Crew cannot invite, delete company, or modify settings
9. `npm run build` — zero TypeScript errors after all GAS references removed

